            "title": "FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cv9GWPIJ1s9Tc7osNE210A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/1f112e5b7533bbacd26b3fa05c237cb5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每年報稅季節一到，成千上萬打工仔又開始頭痕：究竟買唔買扣稅年金？廣告成日話60,000蚊換到$10,200扣稅額，聽落好吸引，但真係咁簡單？唔使心急！如果你想真正玩轉扣稅遊戲，由「稅奴」變「稅王」，只要跟住呢三步走，你就係稅務大師！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第一步：扣稅項目大掃描<br/> 先停一停，唔好急住衝去買年金！想像吓你月入5萬蚊，扣稅項目爆棚：父母免稅額、子女免稅額、醫療開支……全部加埋，分分鐘稅單「清零」！<br/> 但呢個「零稅出關」背後，往往係生活壓力爆燈——家用、供樓、養仔女，稅局都知你慘，先畀你扣番啲錢。<br/> 快啲check吓自己今年有幾多免稅額未用！好多人都漏咗幾萬蚊扣稅機會，結果白白畀稅局食走。呢一步做好，你已經贏咗一半！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e4920b44-a82b-3a1e-a143-63dc59cba3f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第二步：年金扣稅係唔係萬能？<br/> 廣告話買60,000扣到$10,200？聽落好正！但事實上要睇你稅階高低先至知。<br/> 如果你稅階係17%，呢筆錢確實抵玩；但萬一你稅階只係2%或6%，60,000換返幾千蚊就變「雞肋」——扣唔到幾多，仲要鎖死筆錢最少8-10年，萬一中途有急用就麻煩！<br/> 真係划唔來。年金唔係人人適合，唔好被廣告沖昏頭腦，先計清楚自己實際得益幾多！</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第三步：揀年金先至係老闆！<br/> 有得揀先至係老闆！唔同保險公司年金，回報都可以天差地遠。<br/> 有啲產品回報高達4%、保證回本期短至8年，幾年後就見錢返嚟；但有啲保證回報低過3%、綁足10幾年，買咗等於抱住個「爛橙」，全部做足功課，先至唔後悔！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果你都想知道自己需唔需要買年金或者買咩年金好，點擊下面連結交流一下！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">懶人包領取連結🔗⬇️<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://shorturl.at/AzFaB;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://shorturl.at/AzFaB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://shorturl.at/AzFaB</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">想了解更多都可以follow我IG :<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">15分鐘快速線上計稅：<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://forms.gle/RgbAaLCgSbaYN1Y26;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href