            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美元定期存款利率大比拼 邊間銀行最高息？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"628\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_FpVgc3nGOP_Ew9fcF7FWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-11/c6d38500-6004-11ed-af6e-40beea945859\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於美元定期年利率較港元定期年利率更優厚，而且港元與美元掛鈎，可減低一般做外幣定期的匯率風險。我們從多間銀行網站搜尋資料，綜合數據以1萬美元及10萬美元作例子，比較一下本港各大銀行最新定期存款利率！利率表更附有各間銀行定期存款優惠連結，方便大家參考！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9e15c99-b1a1-4a77-b05e-7ccc69e27971-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特朗普公開要求聯儲局「立即」減息，點名主席鮑威爾行動過慢，但聯儲局重申將按經濟數據在議息會議上決定政策。隨中東局勢升溫推高油價，市場對減息預期迅速降溫。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利率期貨顯示，交易員目前僅預期今年12月或有一次減息，9月減息機會已被排除。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛亦將減息預測由6月延後至9月，並指通脹前景較高將限制政策轉向，除非勞動市場顯著轉弱，否則聯儲局短期料維持利率不變。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"債券交易員不再押注聯儲局2026年減息一次的概率為100%\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:債券交易員不再押注聯儲局2026年減息一次的概率為100%;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%832026%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E6%AC%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E7%8E%87%E7%82%BA100-151833300.html\"><strong>債券交易員不再押注聯儲局2026年減息一次的概率為100%</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"2\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特朗普施壓鮑威爾「立即減息 別拖到下次會議！」\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普施壓鮑威爾「立即減息 別拖到下次會議！」;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%